title: On Line Applications and Payments
posting_body: ["At Arrive on University, you'll experience the excitement of big-city life in the heart of the sprawling Dallas metroplex.", 'Whether you commute, study, travel, or enjoy the occasional weekend excursion, our easy access to I-30 and the 75 opens every avenue to elevated living.', 'Our pet-friendly community provides spacious one and two-bedroom floor plans featuring some of the largest living spaces in Dallas.', 'Residents are invited to relax in our pool and resort-style courtyard, enjoy complimentary Wi-Fi in our common areas, and meet their fitness goals in our onsite fitness center.', 'Contact us today to learn more about the unparalleled luxury living experience here at Arrive On University!', 'View Our Floor Plans', '-iMac Work Station', '-Stainless Steel Microwave', '-Controlled Access', '-Disposal', '-Stainless Steel Dishwasher', '-Washer/Dryer Hookup', '-Accepts Electronic Payments', '-Outdoor Pergola and Grilling Station', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Fitness Center', '-Designer Kitchens with Granite Countertops', '-Pets Allowed', 'Call Now or Text', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
